    "body": "The build process should check if we have a git directory (this is not required) and if the current commit is tagged starting with a `v` and then create an empty file called `prerelease.txt` in the top directory. This will cause the build process to create a release binary.\r\n\r\nAt best, we should use a different mechanism that the prerelease.txt file, but we have a requirement that he build has to be possible without git.",
